track_notes: Very nice and good path to the summit.

Track for Haglebu parking -> LA/BU-060 -> LA/BU-136 -> LA/BU-156 -> Haglebu parking.

Path to LA/BU-136 and later to LA/BU-156 is non optimal and in some places very steep and rather dangerous, so do not follow it blindly!
track_title: GPX for tripple activation, where LA/BU-060 is the first summit

track_notes: Winter 2024 track from parking at Haglebu. Heavy track in winter 2024 with lots of snow and ice.
